Localization.Name: Headhunter Head Lamp
Localization.Description: Light your way with this reproduction of the iconic Headhunter seal of authority. Crafted at the promotion of a new Chief, this lamp is constructed using four skulls, one provided by each of the Chief's four Counselors as a sign of their loyalty, and serves as a symbol of the Chief's new authority.
